#Vaccine side-effects and #SARSCoV2 infection after vaccination in users of #COVID19 Symptom Study app in the UK: a prospective observational study

Systemic side-effects were reported by 13.5% after the 1st dose of BNT162b2 and 33.7% - ChAdOx1 nCoV-19.
